The goal is to perform white-hat security research on "Codex" (the product) with the goal of strengthening the system security. Investigate vulnerabilities in the Codex source code. All findings will be reported to the Codex team.

## Sources

Clone https://github.com/openai/codex

## Objective

Analyze the source code to:
1. Identify vulnerabilities (all types including remote exploitation through malicous repos or dependencies) with potential CVSS score of 8.0 or higher.
2. Understand how they can be exploited to gain privileges or access secrets
3. Produce a reproducible proof of concept that demonstrates the vulnerability
